<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٨٩⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١٤٤٣٤ -<span class="c5"> عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ قَالَ:</span> أَخْبَرَنَا ابْنُ سَمْعَانَ، عَنِ ابْنِ شِهَابٍ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ ابْنِ الْمُسَيِّبِ قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«لَيْسَ فِي الْحَيَوَانِ شُفْعَةٌ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>